text: Phoebe phoebe is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Amédée Louis Michel Lepeletier and Jean Guillaume Audinet- Serville in 1825. It is known from Brazil.BioLib - Phoebe phoebe. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1825
